videos.description: St. John's cashes in on a Georgetown turnover as Justin Simon hits a streaking LJ Figueroa, who finesses the breakaway two-handed slam.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Figueroa slams jam for St. John’s) 2019/1/5 ESHEET

videos.headline: Figueroa slams jam for St. John's

videos.description: LJ Figueroa's save out of bounds goes to Shamorie Ponds, who leads the break and lobs an oop to Mustapha Heron for a highlight dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Heron rips rim on St. John's alley-oop) 2019/1/5 ESHEET

videos.headline: Heron rips rim on St. John's alley-oop

videos.description: LJ Figueroa sends a pass from beyond the 3-point line to Justin Simon, who rises high and spikes the dunk.
